headline: Is McCormick’s (MKC) Paris Hilton Tie-Up a Glimpse Into Its Next Brand Chapter?
summary: In January 2026, McCormick & Company, Incorporated announced a two-year collaboration with Paris Hilton and her media company 11:11 Media, centered on a new ad campaign that links its spices, seasonings, and extracts to memorable film and TV moments.
